{
  "texts": [
    "Do I plan my physical activity?",
    "The answer is \"No\".",
    "But singing is imperative, and that's because I enjoy it, and I can honestly say that it has had a remarkable effect on my breathing, and that is the main reason why my consultant gets annoyed [laughs, referring to his earlier joke that he is doing unexpectedly well for his condition and his consultant makes jokes about it].",
    "So, I have aortic stenosis, a licking valve.",
    ". in the atrium."
  ]
}